responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "92A40C28420291D2B8EA6AA4978AA235", "P.16.Month and Day: It has been hard to speak let alone pen my thoughts since my return to Dargal Estate. Isa has died. Aly and the Sodbottoms did their best, but they could not keep the bandits out. Isa was raped and slain. Aly said he alyed he buried her body in the Underwell, but I will bring her to the light of the surface and grace her resting place with roses.")
name: MADD_0012_RWS_RodericsDiary16Page_3
